<div class="page-wrap">
  <div class="page-title">How It Works</div>
  <div class="page-sub">Four inputs. One perfect tape. Zero guesswork.</div>

  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">01</div>
      <h3>Enter your setup</h3>
      <p>IBO speed, draw weight, draw length and arrow weight — or just punch in your chronograph reading if you have one. A chrono reading is always more accurate.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">02</div>
      <h3>Speed is calculated</h3>
      <p>We estimate your real arrow speed using the ATA formula, accounting for all your accessories like peep sight, kisser button, silencers, and drop-away rest.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">03</div>
      <h3>Tape is generated</h3>
      <p>Precise sight movement values are calculated for every yardage increment, scaled exactly to your sight radius. The physics is the same formula pros use.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">04</div>
      <h3>Print and shoot</h3>
      <p>Download the PDF, print at 100% scale (no scaling to fit!), cut along the edge, and stick it to your sight housing. Then verify at the range before season.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

